  <brief_title>The Value of PSP in Predicting Outcome in ICU Surgical Peritonitis Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Diagnostic Accuracy of Pancreatic Stone Protein in Predicting Severe Outcome in Patients With Peritonitis at the Intensive Care Unit</official_title>
